Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria-sama is summoning the Three Phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The master beckons? Whatever for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that Straw Hat\NLuffy has been captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to make a show\Nout of reanimating No. 900!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here? This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Perona-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip it, Kumacy! How many times\Nmust I tell you not to talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're as harsh on Kumacy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beary harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, have you heard?\NThe master is summoning us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They still haven't found us,\Nif you can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we hide here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have much choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew Beast Man was \Ngonna catch up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't realize this was a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for a chance to make\Na break for it. Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went!\NI have something that I'd like to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we have one more\Nintruder on top of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,An intruder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Humming Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They've never failed to catch\Nour prey, not even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We hung out quietly in the ceiling\Nand snatched your friends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll take you to the same\Nplace we took your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Brace yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:11.88,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:17.96,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo ho ho ho, yo ho ho ho
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?! Who's singing that song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, I see everyone really\Ndid disembark onto this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm light!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as you're here, I suppose\Nyou've left me with no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall tell you everything \Nabout this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't a zombie, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're with these pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Verse Humming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...Nock Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Luffy's Emergency Situation!\NThe Ultimate Shadow's Destination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight's not over!\NSwords don't work on zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna pop back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry! I've already dealt with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even zombies have weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the zombie's "soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul?! But I can see it leaving his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's high time you returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...to your rightful master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Tararan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! He took out the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't budging an inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I purified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! He's definitely the\N"Humming Swordsman"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, he wreaked\Nhavoc on Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta tell the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That spider web is strong\Nagainst physical attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but weak against fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It melts right off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They got Straw Hat and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you seem mighty\Nknowledgeable about this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, but I don't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If they've been caught, \Nwe're probably too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me jump under my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have any skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my skull humor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother. He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please put the\Njoking aside and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother! He's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As I already told you,\Nwithout a working rudder,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent decades wandering these seas alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I wanted to escape \Nfrom the Devil's Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at the mercy of the tide\Nbecause of my broken rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go back to about five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Much like you and your crewmates,\NI was "invited" to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Desperate to leave the Florian Triangle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked around this island in hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of finding the parts I \Nneeded to fix my rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anything is down here... Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?! Crap! Crap! Crap! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Freaky! I hate ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All I found were monsters and zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they caught me and\Nbrought me here to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...a martial arts dancer who\Nthey caught before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a type of corpse covered\Nin stitches called a "mario."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghastly giant appeared before them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He peeled the man's shadow off the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...and snip, snip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut the man's shadow off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I questioned my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have any eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for a knuckle sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to let him have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly thereafter, I suffered the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who lost his shadow\Ncollapsed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His severed shadow was stuffed\Ninto the inanimate mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The "mario" corpse got \Nup and started to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows are our "second souls" that are\Nalways with us, moving as we dictate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true of your shadows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, these "souls" always stay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,following your every moment from\Nthe moment you're born until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a giant of a man who captures\Nthem and makes them do his bidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He is one of the Seven Warlords\Nof the Sea, Gecko Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He has eaten the Shadow-Shadow Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A Devil Fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the one who stole your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain man stole my\Nshadow a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sorta thing actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And having lost my shadow, I am no\Nlonger able to exist in the world of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot live under the light of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if you\Nwere hit by the sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was directly hit by sunlight, my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...would be obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he has a corpse, he can use\Na shadow to turn it into a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is that his cohort\Nis the genius surgeon, Dr. Hogback.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He can reconstruct the body,\Nmaking it stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes he uses his medical\Nexpertise to revive the flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of legendary warriors from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has a tremendous collection of mario\Ncurrently preserved in his lab freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hogback...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize the renowned\Ndoctor has been here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,assisting a pirate ever \Nsince he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So those zombies are reanimated corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like he actually\Nrevived the dead, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow provides their\Npersonality and fighting abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of their body depends on\Nthe physical ability of their mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you combine a strong body\Nwith a strong shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it will create an even stronger zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why Moria is eager to get\Nhis hands on wanted men's shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I getcha! No wonder he came after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the deal with Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria's favorite aspect about\Nzombies could be their obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, it's a challenge to\Nkeep powerful warriors in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but our shadows possess\Nthe same abilities as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he has our shadows,\Nhe can toss us troublemakers out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The powerful are quickly returned to\Nthe sea while they're still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, they're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you the best way to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me and do as I instruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You want us to believe you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good sir, I'm shocked to the skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I haven't bickered like\Nthis in decades, so I'm eating it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear you out, so get talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Three Phantoms have gathered together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick! Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn me into the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The future Pirate King...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Untie this rope, you oversized shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Usopp, Nami, Chopper,\NSanji, and Zoro back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hide them, shallot head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This one has lot of fight in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Straw Hat Luffy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hard time believing this is the man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who picked a fight with the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he wearing General Zombie armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it? This is every guy's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You got captured, so don't\Nlecture me about dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Straw Hat Luffy! You've made\Na pretty big name for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're only our third catch so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Pirate Hunter Zoro and some\Nblond guy who didn't have a wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sanji's the only blond in my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Hey, it sounds like\Nthey caught Zoro and Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! And they even have Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did the three monsters\Nhave to be the first to get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who these guys are,\Nbut they're definitely bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what happened\Nto that trio, Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall handing them over\Nto the Risky Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kumacy never got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure they didn't \Nescape on their way over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The casket popped open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush! Dude, don't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Actually--\N--I keep telling you to keep that mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too harsh on Kumacy.\NYou're beary harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the trio that includes my bride caused
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,\Nquite the commotion in your courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about \Nit... Hogback, you pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you've raised your\Nhand against my future bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you not to touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Cindry-chan!\NYou're only adding fuel to the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you standing in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get married, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're killing me! That \Nwas a nasty stray bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they going to do with\NLuffy now that they've caught him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's happened to Sanji and Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in pretty deep doo-doo ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no way Luffy's\Ngonna stay in that cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good! Keep nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says,\Nmy mind is made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman will be my blushing bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Cindry-chan!\NWhy don't you just ignore Absalom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect to get married... ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's two stray bullets in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I'll never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand all your fussing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If those pirates got away,\Nyou can deal with it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I had you gather so we could celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the commemorative creation \Nof a powerful ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, the pirate chewed\Nthrough the cage and is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He chewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...through the cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you capture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to prove dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Absalom! We're indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't catch me, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're multiplying as they dance! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch them and keep them as pets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an epic fail.\NI'm such a loser this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the whole world booing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I've got the punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could be reborn, I'd like to be a clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work on me a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could be reborn,\NI'd like to be a sea cucumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive! Ne-ga-tive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To fall from Pirate King\Nto sea cucumber...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Brutal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him with the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk, I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?! My shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've obtained 300 million\NBerries' worth of might!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can complete the greatest\NSpecial Zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the moment of the \Ncentury, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw his corpse in the Land of Ice,\Nmy body wouldn't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cindry-chan, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to the famous Giant known\Nas the legendary "Continent Puller."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate Ki--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a far cry from your line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Warrior Known as the 'Devil'!!\NThe Moment of Oars' Revival!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
